{
  "texts": [
    "RAG + QD modifies the retrieval stage by introducing question decomposition.",
    "The original query q is transformed into a set of sub-queries {q 1,.",
    ", qn }, and retrieval is performed independently for each element of Q = {q} ∪ {q i }.",
    "The retrieved results are merged, and the top-k passages are selected based on similarity scores.",
    "This setup increases retrieval coverage by capturing information across multiple query aspects."
  ]
}